description: Variation of condition 10 (in accordance with approved drawings) pursuant to planning permission dated 04/01/2016 ref 2015/3470 (Demolition of existing (now demolished) petrol station (Class Sui-Generis) and redevelopment of the site including erection of a 4-7 storey building to provide 71 self-contained residential units (Class C3) (22 x 1 bedrooms, 41 x 2 bedrooms, 8 x 3 bedrooms) with associated cycle parking and landscaping.) to allow variation of approved drawings, consisting of minor changes to the southern corner at lower ground, ground and first floor levels and the removal of two of the residential units.
